A love potion reportedly made\r\nby a witch.\r\n\r\nIt is said that if you mix your\r\nown blood with this potion, the\r\nperson who drinks will become\r\nyour captive.\r\n\r\nIn actual fact, it wasn't a\r\nwitch who created it, but the\r\npeople of Reville, who made a\r\nname for themselves in alchemy,\r\nthough the truth is not widely\r\nrealised.
