\r\n\r\nA mysterious box with nine\r\nkeyholes. Beautifully decorated\r\nand shiny, the box, with or\r\nwithout its contents, holds\r\ngreat value.\r\n\r\nTo open it requires the nine\r\ndifferent keys which fit into\r\neach keyhole, said to have been\r\nscattered throughout the world,\r\nand difficult to find.
