\r\n\r\nThe horn of the god of war,\r\nwhich legend states will summon\r\nhis army of 100, 000 soldiers\r\nwhen blown loudly.\r\n\r\nIn truth, it was used to send\r\ncommands to tens of thousands\r\nof soldiers during historical\r\nbattles, and even if it is\r\nsounded, a divine army will\r\nnot come marching.
