A book containing the secrets\r\nof alchemy, originating from\r\nReville, creators of the\r\nMagicite. As far as can be made\r\nout from the illustrations,\r\nit contains various bits of\r\ninformation such as magic\r\ncircle types to the method of\r\nrefining Magicite, though it is\r\nimpossible to understand unless\r\nyou can decipher the writing\r\nwhich appears to be in some\r\nsort of code.
