The soul of a person who\r\nturned into an ancient giant\r\nwhich had nowhere to go.\r\nThough the flickering flame\r\ngives off a pale glow, it leaves\r\nyou with a sense of melancholy.\r\nOver time it grows smaller and\r\nsmaller until it eventually\r\ndisappears.\r\n\r\nThere is speculation about its\r\nfate after it has disappeared,\r\nsuch as it returning to nothing,\r\nor being called to heaven.
